* Iron Raptor only stood there and let Prowl slide his arm around her, 
giving her a little peck on the cheek. She could feel his love for her and 
felt her own for him as well.
She leaned against him and began to make her way into the ship, holding the 
little kitten in her arms.*

< Just a few scratches.>

* She smiled and put an arm around his shoulders while holding the kitten in 
her other arm.*

< I'm just gald that's all over.>
